## Data Structures

### Comment (object)
    + author_id (string) (required)
    + content (string) (required)
    + created_at (string) (required)
    + id (string) (required)
    + task_id (string) (required)
    + updated_at (string) (required)

### Developer (object)
    + active (boolean) (required)
    + avatar_url (string)
    + created_at (string) (required)
    + email (string) (required)
    + full_name (string) (required)
    + hire_date (string)
    + id (string) (required)
    + role (string) (required)
    + skills (array)
    + team (string)
    + updated_at (string) (required)
    + username (string) (required)

### DeveloperCreated (object)
    + Attributes (array[DeveloperEvent])

### DeveloperDeleted (object)
    + deleted_by (string) (required)
    + developer_id (string) (required)
    + event (string) (required)
    + timestamp (string) (required)

### DeveloperEvent (object)
    + actor (object) (required)
        + id (string) (required)
        + type (string) (required)
    + changes (object)
        Fields that were changed (for update events)
    + developer (string) (required)
    + event (string) (required)
    + timestamp (string) (required)

### DeveloperUpdated (object)
    + Attributes (array[DeveloperEvent])

### EventHeaders (object)
    + correlation-id (string)
        Correlation ID for tracking related events
    + event-id (string)
        Unique identifier for the event
    + event-version (string)
        Version of the event schema
    + source (string)
        Source system that generated the event

### Project (object)
    + budget (number)
    + created_at (string) (required)
    + description (string)
    + end_date (string)
    + id (string) (required)
    + member_count (integer) (required)
    + name (string) (required)
    + owner_id (string) (required)
    + start_date (string)
    + status (string) (required)
    + task_count (integer) (required)
    + updated_at (string) (required)

### ProjectCreated (object)
    + Attributes (array[ProjectEvent])

### ProjectDeleted (object)
    + deleted_by (string) (required)
    + event (string) (required)
    + project_id (string) (required)
    + timestamp (string) (required)

### ProjectEvent (object)
    + actor (object) (required)
        + id (string) (required)
        + type (string) (required)
    + changes (object)
        Fields that were changed (for update events)
    + event (string) (required)
    + project (string) (required)
    + timestamp (string) (required)

### ProjectMemberAdded (object)
    + added_by (string) (required)
    + developer_id (string) (required)
    + event (string) (required)
